      <h2 class="sec-title">FY27 opened with a 568-point gap-up — and closed having given almost all of it back. Breadth was the strongest in weeks, defence stocks surged 6%, GST crossed ₹2 lakh crore for the first time. The index lied. The market did not.</h2>
